Class Cellular

java.lang.Object
  jade.gen.Cellular
All Implemented Interfaces:
Gen
public class Cellular
extends java.lang.Object
implements Gen

This implementation of Gen uses cellular automata to generate interesting cave level. The maps will always be connected either by throwing away disconnected maps for small worlds, or filling in small disconnected parts on large maps.
